// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2943 — Mass File Rename (spacebears)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 75b55986-9bd8-5316-bd38-92836f482b54

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
